description: SUPCASE Beetle Defense Series Hybrid Protective Case provides a stylish but protective shield between your iPad Air and the accidental drop, scrape, or scratch. Made from soft thermoplastic polyurethane and hard polycarbonate materials, SUPCASE Beetle Defense Series Protective Case snaps on for immediate protection.Compatibility:Compatible with iPad Air (iPad 5th Generation), allowing full access to touchscreen, camera, buttons, and ports.NOT COMPATIBLE with iPad 1/2/3/4 and iPad Mini 1st/2nd Generation.Materials:High grade polycarbonate + thermoplastic polyurethane for shock absorption. Front cover with built-in screen protector prevents scratches without compromising sensitivity.Design:Designed with both protection and looks in mind, SUPCASE Beetle Defense Series Full-body Hybrid Case provides shock absorption and scratch prevention while maintaining a sporty profile.- Advanced Front Cover Design for Easy Installation- Built-in Screen Protector without compromising sensitivity- Advanced dual-layer (PC + TPU) design provides great impact and shock resistance and prevents accidental drop, bumps, and shock- Port Cover keeps out debris and dust- Easy access to all features (buttons, camera, speaker, and ports)- Sporty profile and multiple color optionsWhat's in the package?1x SUPCASE Beetle Defense Case for iPad Air
title: SUPCASE Beetle Defense Series for Apple iPad Air Full-body Hybrid Protective Case with Built-in Screen Protector (Black/Black) - Dual Layer Design and Impact Resistant Bumper (Fit iPad 5th Generation)
